OL,4,CVeteran charity runner robbed at
OL,5,Cknifepoint near Burton upon Trent
OL,6, A man running 1,200 miles (1,931km) to
OL,7, raise money for a veterans charity has
OL,8, been mugged at knifepoint.
OL,10,FPhil Hammond, from Leeds, was stopped
OL,11,Fby a man in Barton-under-Needwood, near
OL,12,FBurton upon Trent, on Monday evening,
OL,13,FStaffordshire Police said.
OL,15,FHe was on a footpath by a canal when he
OL,16,Fwas threatened with the knife and
OL,17,Fhanded over #40 before the robber fled.
OL,19,FMr Hammond said he had not been put off
OL,20,Fby the crime and would continue his
OL,21,Fcharity run.
